                  <scopecontent id="aspace_5dad5513529956a9796b668be707ae76">
                     <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                     <p>Salop <lb/> 4 p.; 19 x 15 cm. <lb/> Literary topics and personalities, <lb/> including remarks about Edmund <lb/> Curll, a printer (1675-1747) and <lb/> William Pattison (1706-1727). <lb/> 357/2</p>
                  </scopecontent>
               </c>
            </c>
