                     <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                     <p>Cambridge <lb/> 2 p.; 22 x 17 cm. <lb/> Humorous letter to a friend after an <lb/> "intermission of our epistolary <lb/> correspondence." <lb/> 357/1</p>
                  </scopecontent>
               </c>
            </c>
            <c id="ref19" level="subseries">
               <did>
                  <unittitle>TAYLOR, JOHN, 1704-1766</unittitle>
