                                id="aspace_7b31c4c91794ec03cf63678aa6bdd36e"
                                label="Mixed Materials"
                                localtype="box">1</container>
                  </did>
                  <scopecontent id="aspace_932596cb38533151cf3b9a5572a1ea79">
                     <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                     <p>Salop <lb/> 3 p.; 21 x 16 cm. <lb/> Literary subjects; belittles his own <lb/> creative accomplishments and recalls <lb/> his former complaints about the "sad <lb/> dearth of wit...in these uncouth <lb/> regions"; he corrects himself and <lb/> writes about the "remarkable" manners <lb/> and polish of the area. <lb/> 357/7</p>
                  </scopecontent>
               </c>
            </c>
            <c id="ref22" level="subseries">
               <did>
                  <unittitle>TAYLOR, JOHN, 1704-1766</unittitle>
               </did>
