                     <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                     <p>Salop <lb/> 3 p.; 20 x 15 cm. <lb/> Friendly letter concerns antiquarian <lb/> topics and regrets about a lost note. <lb/> 357/4</p>
                  </scopecontent>
               </c>
            </c>
