                     <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                     <p>Salop <lb/> 3 p.; 21 x 16 cm. <lb/> Chides friend for not returning his <lb/> letter; comments on literary topics <lb/> and criticizes Edmund Curll <lb/> (1675-1747), a printer, and William <lb/> Pattison (1706-1727). <lb/> 357/5</p>
                  </scopecontent>
               </c>
            </c>
