                     <p>Salop <lb/> 3 p.; 21 x 16 <lb/> Discusses the challenges of <lb/> corresponding with himself and <lb/> begins: "I am heartily sorry for yr <lb/> very great mischief you have brought <lb/> upon yr self in desiring to establish <lb/> a correspondence wth me - Why, I am <lb/> afraid you don't know me...." <lb/> 357/3</p>
